Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stage 8
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The League of Black Knights

Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.48,0:00:14.03,Default,2,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Lelouch vie Britannia, 17th in line to the Imperial throne of the Britannian Empire, enters.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.34,0:00:19.91,Default,4,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that Queen Marianne was murdered in Britannia's capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.91,0:00:23.12,Default,5,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a place where terrorists could enter easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.12,0:00:25.45,Default,6,0000,0000,0000,,Then the true suspect is?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.45,0:00:29.57,Default,7,0000,0000,0000,,My, how frightening. The very thought of investigating scares me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.57,0:00:33.45,Default,8,0000,0000,0000,,However, even though his mother has been killed, he shows remarkable strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.45,0:00:35.94,Default,9,0000,0000,0000,,But Lord Lelouch has no standing anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.94,0:00:38.74,Default,10,0000,0000,0000,,The Ashford family, which supported him, is also finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.74,0:00:40.02,Default,11,0000,0000,0000,,What of his younger sister, the Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.02,0:00:41.32,Default,12,0000,0000,0000,,They say that her legs were shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.32,0:00:42.69,Default,13,0000,0000,0000,,And her eyes were wounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.69,0:00:44.79,Default,14,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that it was an ailment of the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.79,0:00:48.18,Default,15,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same thing. A body that cannot be used in the game of politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.98,0:00:52.99,Default,16,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty, my mother has passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.12,0:00:54.57,Default,17,0000,0000,0000,,And what about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.83,0:00:55.46,Default,18,0000,0000,0000,,"What about it"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.97,0:01:00.66,Default,19,0000,0000,0000,,Did you request an audience from the Imperial Emperor of Britannia just to say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.21,0:01:04.36,Default,20,0000,0000,0000,,Bring in the next one. I do not have the time to play with children.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.36,0:01:05.18,Default,22,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.54,0:01:08.96,Default,23,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, your majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.15,0:01:11.09,Default,24,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you not protect mother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.54,0:01:15.02,Default,25,0000,0000,0000,,You are the Emperor, the greatest person in this country, are you not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.02,0:01:16.60,Default,27,0000,0000,0000,,You should have been able to protect her!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.60,0:01:18.95,Default,28,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least you could have visited Nanali.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.95,0:01:20.40,Default,29,0000,0000,0000,,I have no use for the weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.11,0:01:22.17,Default,30,0000,0000,0000,,The weak?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.17,0:01:24.71,Default,31,0000,0000,0000,,That is the true nature of the imperial family.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.32,0:01:30.81,Default,32,0000,0000,0000,,Then I... do not need to be a successor of the throne!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.68,0:01:37.00,Default,33,0000,0000,0000,,I have had enough of following you and being caught up in conflict!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.00,0:01:38.74,Default,34,0000,0000,0000,,You are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:42.43,Default,35,0000,0000,0000,,You have been dead since the day you were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.43,0:01:45.33,Default,36,0000,0000,0000,,Who gave you those clothes that you wear on your back right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.33,0:01:50.02,Default,37,0000,0000,0000,,Your home, your food, even your life...\NI am the one who gave all of that to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.02,0:01:53.45,Default,38,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you have not even once truly been alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.45,0:01:56.05,Default,40,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, you show such insolence?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.77,0:01:59.54,Default,41,0000,0000,0000,,Lelouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:02.63,Default,42,0000,0000,0000,,A dead person like you has no rights.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.63,0:02:05.33,Default,43,0000,0000,0000,,You will go to Japan with Nanali.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.33,0:02:09.51,Default,44,0000,0000,0000,,As a Prince and Princess, you will be good trading material.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.02,0:04:01.32,Default,46,0000,0000,0000,,The seventh generation Knightmare Frame has abilities that are beyond normal...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.32,0:04:04.19,Default,47,0000,0000,0000,,I heard an Eleven is the pilot of that Lancelot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.54,0:04:06.59,Default,48,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. He is an honorary Britannian.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.59,0:04:07.55,Default,49,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.55,0:04:09.94,Default,50,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have him promoted from a Private to a Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.94,0:04:11.25,Default,51,0000,0000,0000,,That should be sufficient.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:14.77,Default,52,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show that I can win without depending on numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.78,0:04:19.65,Default,53,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you fight with your life at stake that you have the right to reign.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.86,0:04:22.32,Default,54,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that reasoning, sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.85,0:04:23.65,Default,54,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.96,0:04:28.46,Default,55,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for making you look at my homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.46,0:04:29.70,Default,56,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.70,0:04:32.87,Default,57,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't attending a normal school up until now, so it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.12,0:04:36.54,Default,59,0000,0000,0000,,The people in the student council are helping me too, but I can't quite get the hang of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.92,0:04:40.52,Default,60,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth, I was a little worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.93,0:04:44.57,Default,61,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering if you would fit in at such an informal school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.57,0:04:46.51,Default,62,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.51,0:04:49.95,Default,63,0000,0000,0000,,But, I happened to meet an old friend of mine, and he opened the doors for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.29,0:04:52.81,Default,64,0000,0000,0000,,Hold this friend dear to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:57.36,Default,65,0000,0000,0000,,If your friendship continues, then it's not a chance meeting, but one that was inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.36,0:04:58.08,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.08,0:04:59.76,Default,67,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why don't you try that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.76,0:05:01.67,Default,68,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:05.33,Default,69,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like your opinion of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.33,0:05:06.24,Default,70,0000,0000,0000,,J-Jam?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.83,0:05:09.01,Default,71,0000,0000,0000,,I got some good blueberries.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.01,0:05:11.82,Default,72,0000,0000,0000,,All right, break it up, break it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.82,0:05:13.29,Default,73,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have to show ourselves today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.29,0:05:16.15,Default,74,0000,0000,0000,,Con-gra-tulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.15,0:05:17.17,Default,75,0000,0000,0000,,That's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.26,0:05:19.48,Default,76,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:22.84,Default,77,0000,0000,0000,,Go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.84,0:05:26.79,Default,78,0000,0000,0000,,Classes are over for today, but it's also important to meet with your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.65,0:05:30.46,Default,79,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can I ask you something important?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.46,0:05:31.68,Default,80,0000,0000,0000,,Hm, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.71,0:05:35.14,Default,81,0000,0000,0000,,Karen, are you hiding something from us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:37.96,Default,82,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. You don't have to hide it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.96,0:05:39.90,Default,84,0000,0000,0000,,Um, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.66,0:05:41.91,Default,85,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.91,0:05:43.37,Default,86,0000,0000,0000,,It won't surprise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.03,0:05:46.15,Default,87,0000,0000,0000,,The other day, I saw it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.06,0:05:50.42,Default,88,0000,0000,0000,,You're seeing Lulu, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.77,0:05:51.37,Default,89,0000,0000,0000,,Lulu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:53.79,Default,90,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I saw you two at the courtyard the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.67,0:05:56.23,Default,91,0000,0000,0000,,No, no wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.23,0:05:58.10,Default,92,0000,0000,0000,,He was the one that started-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.10,0:05:58.98,Default,93,0000,0000,0000,,Lulu started it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.98,0:06:00.79,Default,94,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.79,0:06:03.41,Default,95,0000,0000,0000,,But the other day, when we were trying to catch that cat, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.41,0:06:05.07,Default,96,0000,0000,0000,,That's completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.07,0:06:06.42,Default,97,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I get upset over a mere kiss...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.69,0:06:09.13,Default,98,0000,0000,0000,,"Mere"? Then, you've done more?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:11.37,Default,99,0000,0000,0000,,No! Stop thinking strange things!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.37,0:06:12.97,Default,100,0000,0000,0000,,You're letting your imagination run wild!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:17.69,Default,101,0000,0000,0000,,About that marriage interview...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.38,0:06:21.86,Default,102,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that you want to rebuild the Ashford family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.21,0:06:24.52,Default,103,0000,0000,0000,,But mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:30.53,Default,104,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Disconnected?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.93,0:06:36.22,Default,105,0000,0000,0000,,We have the Saitama Ghetto completely surrounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.03,0:06:39.36,Default,106,0000,0000,0000,,The Fierce Yamato's hideout is somewhere in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.03,0:06:42.79,Default,107,0000,0000,0000,,More than half of the neighboring civilians are cooperating with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.55,0:06:44.28,Default,108,0000,0000,0000,,How shall we proceed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.64,0:06:46.71,Default,109,0000,0000,0000,,How goes the effort to control the civilian populace?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.71,0:06:49.86,Default,109,0000,0000,0000,,The first group will be ready at t-minus two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.86,0:06:51.55,Default,110,0000,0000,0000,,We're ahead of schedule, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.55,0:06:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.84,0:06:56.31,Default,111,0000,0000,0000,,You men were involved in that incident at Shinjuku, were you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.55,0:07:00.17,Default,112,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we are grateful for your mercy Princess Cornelia...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.59,0:07:01.03,Default,113,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I am talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.71,0:07:03.28,Default,114,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it looks similar?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.28,0:07:03.74,Default,115,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.08,0:07:05.69,Default,116,0000,0000,0000,,To what Shinjuku looked like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.87,0:07:11.81,Default,117,0000,0000,0000,,The military is currently conducting a siege on terrorists in Saitama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.81,0:07:15.95,Default,118,0000,0000,0000,,Due to Governor-general's Cornelia presence, there has been a restriction of entry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.65,0:07:22.92,Default,119,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? What's with that scary face?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.05,0:07:26.45,Default,120,0000,0000,0000,,We've received word that the attack will begin in two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.45,0:07:32.57,Default,121,0000,0000,0000,,Residents of the surrounding areas are...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.19,0:07:30.79,Default,122,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she making us announce the time as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.82,0:07:32.84,Default,123,0000,0000,0000,,She's provoking Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:35.76,Default,124,0000,0000,0000,,Zero is a theatrical type of criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.32,0:07:40.43,Default,125,0000,0000,0000,,In order to draw him out, I have created the same situation as Shinjuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.25,0:07:45.35,Default,126,0000,0000,0000,,If he is the overconfident type, he will surely come to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.35,0:07:46.23,Default,127,0000,0000,0000,,Governor-general!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:48.43,Default,128,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, your life may be in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.09,0:07:52.53,Default,129,0000,0000,0000,,In battle, one must risk their own life to take another's.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.54,0:07:56.24,Default,130,0000,0000,0000,,Do you plan on accepting the enemy's challenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.46,0:07:58.55,Default,131,0000,0000,0000,,She went through all that trouble to invite me, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.84,0:08:02.08,Default,132,0000,0000,0000,,And... there are some things that I want to ask Cornelia, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.08,0:08:06.07,Default,133,0000,0000,0000,,Destroying Britannia or finding out who killed your mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.40,0:08:08.33,Default,134,0000,0000,0000,,Which is more important to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.33,0:08:10.27,Default,135,0000,0000,0000,,Those two are one and the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.27,0:08:14.89,Default,136,0000,0000,0000,,Britiannia's Imperial family is in conflict trying to decide the next one who will succeed the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.04,0:08:19.52,Default,137,0000,0000,0000,,No, they are being forced into conflict... by that man!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.52,0:08:22.97,Default,138,0000,0000,0000,,However, that is also Britannia's strength too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.29,0:08:28.13,Default,139,0000,0000,0000,,Because the most successful person who manages to win will become the next Emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.13,0:08:28.92,Default,140,0000,0000,0000,,That is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.24,0:08:31.36,Default,141,0000,0000,0000,,The weak will lose everything and be forced to grovel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.77,0:08:33.86,Default,142,0000,0000,0000,,That's the kind of country that Britannia is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:35.20,Default,143,0000,0000,0000,,That's the kind of world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.56,0:08:38.28,Default,144,0000,0000,0000,,Survival of the fittest is the rule of nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.28,0:08:40.35,Default,145,0000,0000,0000,,If so, then what will happen to Nanali?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.79,0:08:42.86,Default,147,0000,0000,0000,,Does she have to give up just because she is weak?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.47,0:08:45.58,Default,148,0000,0000,0000,,I will never accept that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.86,0:08:48.29,Default,149,0000,0000,0000,,I will erase a world like that-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.90,0:09:00.60,Default,150,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, there's nothing between me and Lelouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.33,0:09:02.32,Default,151,0000,0000,0000,,Lelouch?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.00,0:09:04.32,Default,152,0000,0000,0000,,So, that's that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.93,0:09:06.00,Default,153,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.74,0:09:09.42,Default,154,0000,0000,0000,,Um... do you know where Lelouch is?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.71,0:09:11.82,Default,155,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know where that jerk is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.31,0:09:14.58,Default,157,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go, Lelouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.04,0:09:18.80,Default,158,0000,0000,0000,,It would be a problem if you were to die before you fulfilled your contract with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.80,0:09:21.63,Default,159,0000,0000,0000,,What you're saying and what you're doing seem to be quite different.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.07,0:09:23.62,Default,160,0000,0000,0000,,I won't kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.62,0:09:25.88,Default,161,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just shoot your leg and force you to stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.33,0:09:27.36,Default,162,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.76,0:09:29.54,Default,163,0000,0000,0000,,You can't use Geass, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:33.44,Default,164,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I had assumed as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.44,0:09:36.62,Default,165,0000,0000,0000,,If you could do it yourself, then you wouldn't have asked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.33,0:09:40.76,Default,166,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think that I fear guns?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.03,0:09:42.37,Default,167,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.32,0:09:50.59,Default,168,0000,0000,0000,,I was dead until the moment I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:54.89,Default,169,0000,0000,0000,,A powerless corpse which was lying to itself and pretending to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:10:01.02,Default,170,0000,0000,0000,,A life that lives without doing anything... it's the same as a slow death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.73,0:10:04.29,Default,171,0000,0000,0000,,If I must live as I did before, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:05.02,Default,172,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.57,0:10:12.09,Default,173,0000,0000,0000,,True, there is no meaning to a life like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.73,0:10:14.50,Default,174,0000,0000,0000,,Damnit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.70,0:10:15.80,Default,175,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.80,0:10:17.28,Default,176,0000,0000,0000,,There are children here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.28,0:10:19.19,Default,177,0000,0000,0000,,We've done nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.51,0:10:20.59,Default,178,0000,0000,0000,,That is exactly why!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.99,0:10:25.56,Default,179,0000,0000,0000,,The civilians of this ghetto did not report the presence of terrorists, but hid and protected them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.00,0:10:28.39,Default,180,0000,0000,0000,,That is a crime of treason against the empire!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.76,0:10:33.54,Default,181,0000,0000,0000,,It appears the civilians have been taken care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.54,0:10:34.39,Default,182,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.39,0:10:35.85,Default,183,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.17,0:10:37.18,Default,184,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.18,0:10:37.69,Default,185,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.44,0:10:43.05,Default,186,0000,0000,0000,,To all troops: We will now begin the operation to destroy the Saitama Ghetto.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.04,0:10:48.18,Default,187,0000,0000,0000,,All troops, line up in formation one!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.43,0:11:02.55,Default,188,0000,0000,0000,,Why does Princess Cornelia not give us the order to attack as well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:04.31,Default,189,0000,0000,0000,,It's because there's an orange with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.21,0:11:07.81,Default,190,0000,0000,0000,,You should be grateful that you got off so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.26,0:11:11.64,Default,191,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, our path has been closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.64,0:11:13.81,Default,192,0000,0000,0000,,But, that was Zero's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.01,0:11:14.95,Default,193,0000,0000,0000,,That again?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.47,0:11:17.06,Default,194,0000,0000,0000,,Zero...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.74,0:11:19.74,Default,194,0000,0000,0000,,Was that student really his ally?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.74,0:11:21.93,Default,195,0000,0000,0000,,The first four blocks have been secured. Seventh and eighth units report no casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.61,0:11:27.60,Default,196,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.94,0:11:31.40,Default,197,0000,0000,0000,,Even though Cornelia replaced Clovis, Britannia hasn't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.20,0:11:34.64,Default,198,0000,0000,0000,,Which unit are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.08,0:11:36.84,Default,199,0000,0000,0000,,State your unit name and ID.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.23,0:11:39.95,Default,200,0000,0000,0000,,I am Daniel Toles of the 3rd Reconnaissance unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.54,0:11:42.97,Default,201,0000,0000,0000,,I have acquired this from the terrorists.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.97,0:11:44.76,Default,202,0000,0000,0000,,Would it be possible for you to take this to headquarters?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.64,0:11:47.70,Default,203,0000,0000,0000,,A disk, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.70,0:11:49.94,Default,204,0000,0000,0000,,But, before that, I'll have to check your ID.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.30,0:11:51.53,Default,205,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.53,0:11:56.11,Default,206,0000,0000,0000,,But, before that, I would also like to have your Sutherland.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.18,0:12:04.52,Default,207,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Handle it with care.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.20,0:12:06.70,Default,209,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.26,0:12:12.51,Default,210,0000,0000,0000,,The outer area has been taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.51,0:12:14.53,Default,211,0000,0000,0000,,So we can't even try to give one last push?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.53,0:12:17.37,Default,212,0000,0000,0000,,The subway's stopped running and the farm roads are being heavily patrolled.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.37,0:12:19.08,Default,213,0000,0000,0000,,What about backup from Akabane or Jouyou?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.08,0:12:20.99,Default,214,0000,0000,0000,,Even with backup we wouldn't stand a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.99,0:12:21.79,Default,215,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.20,0:12:23.18,Default,216,0000,0000,0000,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.18,0:12:24.85,Default,217,0000,0000,0000,,What about Toda or the Kawaguchi route?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.85,0:12:26.24,Default,218,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly... this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.46,0:12:31.94,Default,219,0000,0000,0000,,I am... Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.94,0:12:32.81,Default,220,0000,0000,0000,,Zero?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.81,0:12:33.94,Default,221,0000,0000,0000,,Zero, as in...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.14,0:12:36.75,Default,222,0000,0000,0000,,You should have heard about Shinjuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.75,0:12:38.27,Default,223,0000,0000,0000,,Obey me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.27,0:12:39.90,Default,224,0000,0000,0000,,If you do, I will save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.68,0:12:43.17,Default,225,0000,0000,0000,,B12, suppression complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.17,0:12:44.54,Default,226,0000,0000,0000,,F7, there is no sign of the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.50,0:12:48.37,Default,228,0000,0000,0000,,Group Gordon, please move to position 516.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.54,0:12:46.81,Default,227,0000,0000,0000,,D24, all enemies have been eliminated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.37,0:12:50.94,Default,229,0000,0000,0000,,Yes my Lord. Moving to 516.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.12,0:12:55.29,Default,230,0000,0000,0000,,No action yet. Is that Zero guy coming or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.29,0:12:57.58,Default,231,0000,0000,0000,,He's just another terrorist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.21,0:13:01.17,Default,232,0000,0000,0000,,They came! They really came!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:02.42,Default,233,0000,0000,0000,,It's just as Zero said!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.39,0:13:09.92,Default,234,0000,0000,0000,,Now, how about I lure Cornelia out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.33,0:13:12.10,Default,235,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I can catch them off guard...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.98,0:13:15.22,Default,236,0000,0000,0000,,R1, R2, continue to fall back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.75,0:13:18.04,Default,237,0000,0000,0000,,Lead the enemy out to N2's position.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.43,0:13:20.64,Default,238,0000,0000,0000,,B7, fire at two o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.96,0:13:23.82,Default,239,0000,0000,0000,,P5, open fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.24,0:13:27.88,Default,240,0000,0000,0000,,Group Geshtar, signal lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.88,0:13:29.96,Default,241,0000,0000,0000,,G47, enemies spotted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.96,0:13:32.33,Default,242,0000,0000,0000,,Group Hazinski engaging combat. They seemed to be ambushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:36.04,Default,243,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that the enemy has captured and used our Sutherlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.16,0:13:38.08,Default,244,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same thing that happened in Shinjuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.08,0:13:39.92,Default,245,0000,0000,0000,,Has Zero arrived then?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:43.51,Default,246,0000,0000,0000,,N2, fire at three o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.63,0:13:45.70,Default,247,0000,0000,0000,,R4, fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.88,0:13:48.46,Default,248,0000,0000,0000,,N1, start from the ones on the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.46,0:13:52.29,Default,249,0000,0000,0000,,All right. P3, destroy the bridge and cut off their route.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.93,0:14:01.87,Default,250,0000,0000,0000,,Point 17 has been lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.87,0:14:03.29,Default,251,0000,0000,0000,,Group Haley, signals lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.29,0:14:04.48,Default,252,0000,0000,0000,,So that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.82,0:14:06.99,Default,253,0000,0000,0000,,Order all troops to retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.99,0:14:08.71,Default,254,0000,0000,0000,,Any more casualties are meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.71,0:14:09.73,Default,255,0000,0000,0000,,A withdrawal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.73,0:14:11.33,Default,256,0000,0000,0000,,I beg your pardon, but we can still fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.67,0:14:13.49,Default,257,0000,0000,0000,,You can't fight like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.03,0:14:15.40,Default,258,0000,0000,0000,,This is an order for all troops.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.40,0:14:17.66,Default,259,0000,0000,0000,,Move to the ghetto outskirts as quickly as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:20.83,Default,260,0000,0000,0000,,Don't break your formation! Move to the ghetto outskirts as quickly as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:23.02,Default,261,0000,0000,0000,,What's this... that was no challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.64,0:14:28.37,Default,262,0000,0000,0000,,If I mingle in with the retreating troops, Cornelia, I'll be right next to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:30.76,Default,263,0000,0000,0000,,The conditions to strike were cleared sooner than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.01,0:14:35.86,Default,264,0000,0000,0000,,You can't fight against your blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:38.80,Default,265,0000,0000,0000,,But, those types are dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.80,0:14:40.69,Default,266,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder which path he will take.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.19,0:14:44.32,Default,267,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.81,0:14:46.78,Default,268,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.80,0:14:53.24,Default,269,0000,0000,0000,,So Lulu was here before this area was developed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.54,0:14:54.62,Default,270,0000,0000,0000,,Were you neighbors?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:55.41,Default,271,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:56.22,Default,272,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.22,0:14:59.05,Default,273,0000,0000,0000,,Me? I guess it's similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.88,0:15:03.20,Default,274,0000,0000,0000,,Lulu didn't seem very serious, didn't like hard work, and felt kind of stuck-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.20,0:15:06.95,Default,275,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth, I didn't like him very much when I first met him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.99,0:15:11.51,Default,276,0000,0000,0000,,But I saw a traffic accident the first year of high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.94,0:15:16.23,Default,277,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how you looked at it, the one at fault was the guy who hit them from behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.23,0:15:18.68,Default,278,0000,0000,0000,,But nobody tried to help them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.68,0:15:19.52,Default,279,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.21,0:15:27.68,Default,280,0000,0000,0000,,Lulu didn't look like he was proud of it nor was he laughing at it,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.68,0:15:29.99,Default,281,0000,0000,0000,,but rather, he looked bored as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.31,0:15:33.64,Default,282,0000,0000,0000,,And I thought to myself, "I wonder what he's thinking about."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.64,0:15:35.10,Default,283,0000,0000,0000,,"What is it that he wants to do?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.45,0:15:38.84,Default,284,0000,0000,0000,,So then I got curious, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.77,0:15:41.08,Default,285,0000,0000,0000,,You began to like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.93,0:15:45.88,Default,286,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.14,0:15:48.14,Default,287,0000,0000,0000,,Love is nice, isn't it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.00,0:15:53.03,Default,288,0000,0000,0000,,Cornelia.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.66,0:15:55.35,Default,288,0000,0000,0000,,The one who will lose is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:15:57.72,Default,289,0000,0000,0000,,I will be the one to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:15:58.52,Default,290,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.52,0:15:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.68,0:16:02.10,Default,291,0000,0000,0000,,You are the Goddess of Victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.36,0:16:03.27,Default,292,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.27,0:16:04.93,Default,293,0000,0000,0000,,My knight, Gilford.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.93,0:16:07.28,Default,294,0000,0000,0000,,I thank you for summoning me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.64,0:16:13.75,Default,295,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I have Geass, going in with this much security is too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.11,0:16:17.31,Default,296,0000,0000,0000,,As with Clovis, I'll need to find an opening and catch her off guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.44,0:16:20.55,Default,298,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? The student council room?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.55,0:16:23.21,Default,299,0000,0000,0000,,The meeting for the cat festival should be tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.71,0:16:28.71,Default,300,0000,0000,0000,,Karen says that's not true, but it kind of looked like she was pretending to be mad to cover up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.95,0:16:32.47,Default,301,0000,0000,0000,,That's why it's best to ask him directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.85,0:16:34.81,Default,302,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask him what he thinks of you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.09,0:16:36.53,Default,303,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! You'd go that far?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.85,0:16:38.23,Default,304,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I can word it nicely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.23,0:16:39.68,Default,305,0000,0000,0000,,No, you CAN'T!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:42.98,Default,306,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.19,0:16:44.61,Default,307,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, just let me do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.61,0:16:45.74,Default,308,0000,0000,0000,,If I do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.74,0:16:46.98,Default,309,0000,0000,0000,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.98,0:16:48.58,Default,310,0000,0000,0000,,I can handle this, I can-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:51.36,Default,312,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.06,0:16:56.62,Default,313,0000,0000,0000,,Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.33,0:16:58.51,Default,313,0000,0000,0000,,Did that hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.51,0:16:59.24,Default,314,0000,0000,0000,,Quite.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.31,0:17:06.46,Default,315,0000,0000,0000,,You're must be desperate, Cornelia, trying to mobilize your personal unit to take back the upper hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.53,0:17:08.36,Default,317,0000,0000,0000,,This is Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.78,0:17:12.69,Default,318,0000,0000,0000,,N1, change back to the original signal and pretend to be a Britannian soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.69,0:17:13.59,Default,320,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.49,0:17:15.87,Default,321,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be the bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.63,0:17:20.42,Default,322,0000,0000,0000,,There is a Knightmare which is emitting a signal that has been left behind within the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.71,0:17:22.03,Default,323,0000,0000,0000,,Are they unable to send a message?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.03,0:17:23.02,Default,324,0000,0000,0000,,What of the relief party?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:24.02,Default,325,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.27,0:17:25.07,Default,326,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.07,0:17:26.99,Default,327,0000,0000,0000,,He may be held captive by the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.99,0:17:28.91,Default,328,0000,0000,0000,,I told them to retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.28,0:17:32.19,Default,329,0000,0000,0000,,I have no use for a fighter who cannot obey my orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.19,0:17:33.46,Default,330,0000,0000,0000,,That's that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.46,0:17:34.05,Default,331,0000,0000,0000,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.51,0:17:36.85,Default,332,0000,0000,0000,,Complete the mission, even at the cost of their life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.27,0:17:39.28,Default,333,0000,0000,0000,,If they are under me, this is something that they should know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.72,0:17:41.03,Default,334,0000,0000,0000,,Yes your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:45.50,Default,335,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! Can't you tell by the signal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.50,0:17:46.20,Default,336,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your ally!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.07,0:17:49.63,Default,337,0000,0000,0000,,D-Damnit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.42,0:18:00.55,Default,338,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't check his identity?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.87,0:18:04.85,Default,339,0000,0000,0000,,Then... N2, emit your signal and retreat to the hospital area.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.29,0:18:08.23,Default,340,0000,0000,0000,,R1, R2, wait around. Ambush the enemy as they pursue.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.43,0:18:09.89,Default,341,0000,0000,0000,,Another signal, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.22,0:18:13.28,Default,342,0000,0000,0000,,Which means there is an ambush right ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.28,0:18:15.16,Default,343,0000,0000,0000,,Gloucester, go around the building and encircle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:16.89,Default,344,0000,0000,0000,,They're not falling for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.51,0:18:18.57,Default,344,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.57,0:18:21.24,Default,345,0000,0000,0000,,R1, R2, break off the ambush and retreat immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.41,0:18:25.56,Default,346,0000,0000,0000,,Gloucester, we have reached the indicated location.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.56,0:18:26.92,Default,347,0000,0000,0000,,No enemy troops spotted!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.20,0:18:29.10,Default,348,0000,0000,0000,,So they've read my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.10,0:18:31.75,Default,349,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I really am fighting against Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.26,0:18:34.30,Default,350,0000,0000,0000,,P2, N3, cut around behind the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.03,0:18:36.54,Default,351,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Respond!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.26,0:18:38.85,Default,352,0000,0000,0000,,P2, N3!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.85,0:18:39.80,Default,353,0000,0000,0000,,Damnit...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:41.68,Default,354,0000,0000,0000,,B1, B5, you guys go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.80,0:18:43.00,Default,355,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotta be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.00,0:18:46.09,Default,356,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that we could win against Cornelia's personal unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.29,0:18:50.74,Default,357,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! We surrender!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:52.11,Default,358,0000,0000,0000,,We won't resist!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.11,0:18:53.13,Default,359,0000,0000,0000,,Spare us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.43,0:18:54.27,Default,360,0000,0000,0000,,Kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.03,0:19:00.07,Default,361,0000,0000,0000,,P6, P8, what's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.87,0:19:02.66,Default,362,0000,0000,0000,,B7, go back and cover N4!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.05,0:19:04.15,Default,363,0000,0000,0000,,This is B7.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.15,0:19:05.52,Default,364,0000,0000,0000,,I've found prey here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.52,0:19:06.62,Default,365,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take this one out first!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.75,0:19:08.33,Default,366,0000,0000,0000,,No! That's a decoy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.55,0:19:09.90,Default,368,0000,0000,0000,,B7! Obey my commands!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.24,0:19:11.54,Default,369,0000,0000,0000,,What're you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:12.63,Default,370,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't take it out now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.77,0:19:13.55,Default,371,0000,0000,0000,,Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.55,0:19:15.46,Default,372,0000,0000,0000,,B7! They're coming from above!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.09,0:19:19.88,Default,373,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.62,0:19:23.08,Default,374,0000,0000,0000,,B8, status report.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.08,0:19:24.45,Default,375,0000,0000,0000,,There's no status-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.64,0:19:26.59,Default,376,0000,0000,0000,,B8!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.59,0:19:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damnit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.65,0:19:30.04,Default,377,0000,0000,0000,,Those who are left, report in order from P!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.99,0:19:32.39,Default,378,0000,0000,0000,,Mission complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.39,0:19:34.63,Default,379,0000,0000,0000,,All troops move into formation four.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.63,0:19:36.27,Default,380,0000,0000,0000,,They were overwhelmed?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.27,0:19:37.57,Default,381,0000,0000,0000,,This easily?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.25,0:19:39.94,Default,382,0000,0000,0000,,This hasn't been much of a game at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.55,0:19:43.39,Default,383,0000,0000,0000,,So it didn't go the same way as Shinjuku, did it, Zero?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.92,0:19:45.82,Default,384,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe it was someone mimicking his actions?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.13,0:19:47.01,Default,385,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.01,0:19:47.86,Default,386,0000,0000,0000,,We'll know soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.25,0:19:51.61,Default,387,0000,0000,0000,,This level of organization... it's far too different!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.61,0:19:53.97,Default,388,0000,0000,0000,,A command to all Knightmare pilots.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.27,0:19:56.27,Default,389,0000,0000,0000,,Open your hatches and show your faces!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.24,0:19:58.80,Default,390,0000,0000,0000,,Cornelia!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.23,0:20:01.33,Default,391,0000,0000,0000,,I repeat:
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.72,0:20:04.64,Default,392,0000,0000,0000,,All pilots, open your hatches and show your faces!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.83,0:20:07.31,Default,393,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm forced to show myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.87,0:20:11.92,Default,394,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I don't have Zero's mask, my true face will be revealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.23,0:20:13.23,Default,395,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.69,0:20:16.07,Default,396,0000,0000,0000,,Using Geass...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.07,0:20:16.75,Default,397,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.14,0:20:19.44,Default,398,0000,0000,0000,,Unless I looked directly at my opponent, it won't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.88,0:20:21.58,Default,400,0000,0000,0000,,If the opponent is a Knightmare...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.58,0:20:23.82,Default,401,0000,0000,0000,,Which means... I could still use the other soldiers or pilots...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.07,0:20:28.28,Default,402,0000,0000,0000,,No way! There're too many opponents. How would I make them face me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.28,0:20:30.07,Default,403,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.07,0:20:31.58,Default,404,0000,0000,0000,,I should just say who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.58,0:20:33.36,Default,405,0000,0000,0000,,But, the Knightmare is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.36,0:20:36.01,Default,406,0000,0000,0000,,Then I should launch a front attack and force my way through!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.33,0:20:37.62,Default,407,0000,0000,0000,,That's not possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.62,0:20:40.58,Default,408,0000,0000,0000,,Against Cornelia's personal unit, that's suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.58,0:20:42.63,Default,409,0000,0000,0000,,Open your hatch. It's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.81,0:20:45.72,Default,411,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Hurry up and open your hatch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.72,0:20:48.81,Default,413,0000,0000,0000,,Well, my hatch broke during the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.81,0:20:49.78,Default,414,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.78,0:20:51.04,Default,415,0000,0000,0000,,Then I will open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.87,0:20:52.92,Default,416,0000,0000,0000,,Turn your back towards me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.63,0:20:55.52,Default,417,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.80,0:20:57.91,Default,418,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.81,0:20:59.89,Default,419,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.89,0:21:01.73,Default,420,0000,0000,0000,,It's Zero! We've spotted Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.19,0:21:10.45,Default,422,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? As I thought, this is how Zero acts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.45,0:21:11.45,Default,423,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.63,0:21:12.65,Default,424,0000,0000,0000,,Capture him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.65,0:21:14.20,Default,425,0000,0000,0000,,Groups 3 and 5, follow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.20,0:21:16.33,Default,426,0000,0000,0000,,Image saved, objective confirmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.68,0:21:18.13,Default,427,0000,0000,0000,,All I can do now is pray!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.33,0:21:18.13,Default,428,0000,0000,0000,,Capture him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.55,0:21:20.37,Default,428,0000,0000,0000,,Cut around behind him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.37,0:21:21.71,Default,429,0000,0000,0000,,Firing squad, fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.12,0:21:24.75,Default,431,0000,0000,0000,,He fell!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.14,0:21:26.93,Default,432,0000,0000,0000,,Princess, what should we do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.17,0:21:27.78,Default,433,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.22,0:21:29.73,Default,434,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that this stunt is part of a trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.73,0:21:33.00,Default,435,0000,0000,0000,,That's possible. We don't know whether it's really him or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.47,0:21:38.19,Default,437,0000,0000,0000,,What is clear now is that he seems to be a person with a large amount of pride, just as you theorized.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.33,0:21:40.10,Default,439,0000,0000,0000,,Then pursuing him is meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.43,0:21:41.02,Default,440,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.02,0:21:46.36,Default,441,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that he showed himself to us most likely means that he has prepared an escape route.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.52,0:21:48.86,Default,442,0000,0000,0000,,So he has placed protection upon himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.33,0:21:52.47,Default,443,0000,0000,0000,,She's of a totally different level compared to Clovis...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.47,0:21:53.95,Default,444,0000,0000,0000,,So this is Cornelia?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.41,0:22:02.67,Default,445,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.13,0:22:05.80,Default,446,0000,0000,0000,,I told you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.80,0:22:07.30,Default,447,0000,0000,0000,,If you die, it's a problem for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.55,0:22:08.97,Default,448,0000,0000,0000,,The conditions were the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.97,0:22:10.01,Default,449,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.01,0:22:11.31,Default,450,0000,0000,0000,,You are quite a sore loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.70,0:22:14.97,Default,451,0000,0000,0000,,A certain power is required in order to make full use of these "conditions".
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.56,0:22:17.64,Default,452,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll obtain it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.81,0:22:22.21,Default,453,0000,0000,0000,,An army of my own which will not lose to Britannia.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.22,0:22:25.01,Default,454,0000,0000,0000,,A group of people, a nation!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.03,0:23:57.82,Preview,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,Who is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.35,0:24:00.37,Preview,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,People who can work for me as my army.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.00,0:24:03.21,Preview,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,At this time... if only Suzaku were here...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.66,0:24:04.79,Preview,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't look back!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.22,0:24:06.79,Preview,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,He's a Britannian soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.33,0:24:10.70,Preview,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he doesn't come out on the battlefield, he's on my enemy's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.26,0:24:13.94,Preview,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,Then, the answer I should choose is...
